summary: i love how people claim to be lgbt allies and are accepting when their friends come out but then trash andi mack because “young...
body:
i love how people claim to be lgbt allies and are accepting when their friends come out but then trash andi mack because “young kids shouldn’t be learning about gay stuff that young!” i was sitting at lunch reminiscing on old disney channel and complaining about the new stuff, but defending andi mack. and a friend, who claims to be an lgbt ally, literally said that. like? what?? if they’re too young to learn about gay stuff then why learn of straight stuff? nobody had a problem when straight people got full storylines and arcs and onscreen kisses (which we all know tyrus isn’t gonna get), but nobody complained? so here’s the thing:

you’re not

an ally

if you

don’t support

lgbt

characters

on children’s shows
